metadata.name: Cascade Genesis Honorary Bidder Token
metadata.description:
Cascade is a novel generative art collection portraying patterns in the human proteome. Each piece represents a unique protein, with properties derived from the protein's amino acid sequence, the cellular compartment where the protein localizes to, and the biological process that the protein is involved in.

This honorary token was sent to bidders of our Genesis Collection: https://foundation.app/collection/cg-13b6 

We greatly appreciate all of our supporters and those that placed bids on our original NFT collection. 

Please reference our terms of usage: https://tinkrng.mypinata.cloud/ipfs/QmRxp3XC4sGfttuMdgLQXWv9YZaocpfCs8UFEUGxhkTVY1
